                <div style={{fontSize:12,color:C.gray300,lineHeight:1.7}}>Platinum members earn 2% of the revenue generated from their referrals, paid quarterly. If a Platinum member has referred 15 customers who collectively spend $45,000/year with JT Plumbing, that member receives $900/year in cash — just for telling their friends about you. This creates a financial incentive to KEEP referring forever. No other trades company does this. It turns your best customers into paid ambassadors with aligned incentives. They want your business to succeed because they literally profit from it.</div>
