                        <div style={{fontSize:13,color:C.gray300,marginTop:6,lineHeight:1.7}}>{"You're getting "+target.ch.leadsPerMonth+" leads/mo but only booking "+target.ch.bookingRate+"% ("+currentBooked+" jobs). If you push booking rate to 60% through faster response times and better phone scripts, that's "+improvedBooked+" jobs — "+addedJobs+" extra jobs generating $"+addedRev?.toLocaleString?.()??"0"+" additional revenue. No extra ad spend required."}</div>
